\n<\N[3]>Wow... What a messy room. It's like there's no
organization at all...

\n<sine:ω>ω: Wow, it's so messy! It's rude to say that! This
is a perfect layout! Ordinary people wouldn't
understand, though lol

\n<\N[3]>There's also a time limit... If I have to
investigate everything, it's going to be quite
challenging.

\n<sine:ω>My perfect plan can't possibly fail♪ After
all, I am the strongest, sine:ω-sama☆

\n<sine:ω>\C[24]It's not easy to search with this
number of items, you know?... Ah! Don't get close
to the \C[2]locker\C[24]!

\n<sine:ω>\C[24]I have important things and clothes,
you know! If you go snooping around my underwear
or anything, I'll expose you as a genuine pervert
on the internet! LOL

\n<\N[3]>...I have no interest in children's underwear. If
it comes to this, I'll investigate everything one
by one! Don't underestimate the police's sense of
smell!

\n<\N[3]>(By the way, there's a spot where the drone is
freezing up for some reason... Let me investigate
it a bit.)
